---
title: Steak with Chimichurri with Spinach-Arugula Salad
description: Originating in South America, chimichurri is a vibrant green herb sauce that pairs perfectly with tender slices of steak. The meat’s the star of this dish, so we keep it simple by pairing it with an elegant feta, tomato and broccoli salad.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/steaks-et-sauce-chimichurri-8c96dac2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/steak-with-chimichurri-64ad29f8451ebaadbd04fe18-0ffda258.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipes/steak-with-chimichurri-64ad29f8451ebaadbd04fe18
servings: 2
